726459f-a.title: Queens: Cypress Avenue - Myrtle Avenue
726459f-a.text:
Cypress Ave. (tracks thereon), south side, east of Myrtle Ave.
(foreground not seen), showing in the center of the view Captain Louis
Dohling's roadhouse.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

726400f-a.text:
Cornelia Street, east side, at the intersections of Myrtle Ave.,
(left) and Cypress Ave. (righte, showing the former Kreuscher's
Hotel remodeled.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

726457f-a.text:
Cypress Ave. (tracks thereon), at and adjoining the S.E. corner of

April 1925.
